      "@type": [
        "uco-observable:ObservableObject",
        "uco-core:UcoObject"
      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Trade Secret Category 2",
      "uco-core:description": "Documents including details of the design, performance, and operation of Google's custom designed TPU chips, TPU machines, and TPU systems. Exemplar exhibit file titles from the verdict form: Accelerators; Ghostlite; Ghostlite Multi-host Software Enablement Program Kickoff; ViperLite; ViperLitePod; ViperLitePod System Introduction (trial exhibits 374-380). Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 37"
    },
