      "@type": [
        "uco-observable:ObservableObject",
        "uco-core:UcoObject"
      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Trade Secret Category 3",
      "uco-core:description": "Design documents for Google's TPU software that managed the hardware and resources within a TPU, facilitated communication between TPUs, and allocated and managed collections of interconnected TPUs to different workloads. Exemplar exhibit file titles from the verdict form: Cloud TPU; Ghostfish Software Review; ICI Resilient Slice; XLA/TPU; Slice Builder; Slice Creation Algorithms; MegaScale XLA; Megascale Networking; JAX+Pathways; XOR PRD; TPU Fungibility/ACU Roadmap (trial exhibits 381-399). Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 38"
    },
