      "uco-core:name": "Trade Secret Category 4",
      "uco-core:description": "Documents including details of the design, performance, and operation of Google's custom GPU machines and GPU systems. Exemplar exhibit file titles from the verdict form: AdAstra-Board / Hardware / Mechanical / NetworkTopology / Storage; BigRig; Endurance-B Hardware Design Doc; Endurance GPU tray fans; Rack - Jolt, Zoid2; H100 Competitive Analysis (trial exhibits 400-410). Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 39"
