        "uco-core:UcoObject"
      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Trade Secret Category 7",
      "uco-core:description": "Design documents for Google's software to implement its high performance and cloud networking on its SmartNIC. Exemplar exhibit file titles from the verdict form: Raptor Multi-NIC; RDMA on-NIC SW architecture; Andromeda3.0; CloudRDMA Overview / Arch / DeepDive series; Diorite-gHMA / OCM / Routing / Topology; HMA RDMA Support; Pony Express Use Cases (trial exhibits 441-462). Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 42"
