      "uco-core:description": "Periodic uploads of Google Confidential Information \u2014 including all seven trade secret categories \u2014 via the Apple Notes-to-PDF method that evaded immediate detection. Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 17",
