      "uco-core:name": "Ding circulates the PRC-policy PowerPoint to Zhisuan employees and investors (2023-11-17)",
      "uco-core:description": "Presentation citing the PRC State Council's 2017 AI development notice and the CAC-sponsored Interim Measures for generative AI. Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 24",
