      "uco-core:name": "Ding uploads additional files to Ding Account 2 from the PRC (2023-12-02)",
      "uco-core:description": "Upload from the Google network to a second personal Google Drive account while Ding was in the PRC \u2014 the activity Google's monitoring detected. Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 27",
