      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Colleague scans Ding's badge to simulate his presence (2023-12-04 to 2023-12-08)",
      "uco-core:description": "At Ding's request, another Google employee scanned Ding's access badge on December 4, 6, and 8, 2023, making it appear Ding was working from his U.S. office while he was in the PRC. Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 31",
