        "uco-core:UcoObject"
      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Ding signs the Self-Deletion Affidavit without disclosing the exfiltration (2023-12-08)",
      "uco-core:description": "After Google detected the Account 2 upload, Ding told a Google investigator the files were evidence of his work and he had no intention of leaving Google, then signed the affidavit \u2014 concealing the 1,000+ prior uploads and his Rongshu and Zhisuan affiliations. Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 27",
      "uco-action:performer": {
        "@id": "urn:uuid:aeeaf703-8a4a-554b-9882-0228790fb782"
