      "uco-core:name": "Ding books a one-way ticket from San Francisco to Beijing (2023-12-14)",
      "uco-core:description": "China Southern Airlines flight scheduled to depart 2024-01-07, booked unbeknownst to Google. Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), para. 28",
