      "uco-core:name": "Original Count One: Theft of Trade Secrets (Chip architecture and software design specifications for TPU version 4)",
      "uco-core:description": "Original indictment count charging theft of Chip architecture and software design specifications for TPU version 4 on or about and between 2022-06-01 and 2023-04-17; superseded by the category-based counts of the superseding indictments. Source: PACER Doc 1 (indictment), count table",
      "legalproc:statuteCitation": "18 U.S.C. \u00a7 1832(a)(1), (2), and (3)",
      "legalproc:countLabel": "Count One (original)",
