      "uco-core:name": "Count Fourteen: Economic Espionage (Trade Secret Category 7)",
      "uco-core:description": "On or about and between 2022-05-21 and 2024-01-13, in the Northern District of California and elsewhere, Ding, intending or knowing that the offense would benefit a foreign government, foreign instrumentality, or foreign agent, knowingly stole, copied, transmitted, and possessed without authorization Trade Secret Category 7: Design documents for Google's software to implement its high performance and cloud networking on its SmartNIC. Source: PACER Doc 140 (second_superseding_indictment), counts table",
