      "uco-core:description": "Trial on the fourteen counts of the Second Superseding Indictment; the verdict form (Doc 367) records unanimous findings for Ding on each count, with per-category identification of the documents the jury unanimously agreed constitute trade secrets. Presiding juror signed 2026-01-29. Sentencing had not occurred in the modeled record. Source: PACER Doc 367 (jury_verdict), pp. 1-15",
